{"tid":1137291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"批麥當勞標誌像女性胸部 女向法院提告要求精神賠償","createTime":"2019-05-03T15:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T15:55:54.000Z","uid":101419,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e961058ecac40b6706c697cd55b2fa09c4cba1aa","tid":1137291,"uid":101419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:42:31.000Z","msg":"據俄羅斯《uralinform》報導，俄羅斯女子科羅溫科娃( Anastasia Korovenkova)認為，麥當勞惡意使用女性大乳房當商標，損害女性消費者的精神狀態。<br />\n<br />\n她認為並非所有俄羅斯人都有大乳房，因此乳房小的女性會認為自己不正常。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，如果科羅溫科娃成功的話，那她可以獲得1萬盧布(約641令吉)的精神賠償費。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v6OssWm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv6OssWm.png&h=f886cdfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你啲女權撚真係愈黎愈撚顛<br />\n千幾蚊港幣就係你成個人嘅價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc786049572fa0c66bf7ed5fc5185c7ba23b645e","tid":1137291,"uid":240954,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKwJLLQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKwJLLQ.png&h=0ba63665&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e42a7d365e5c708db4e5f84fd3d95b4fb573b4a","tid":1137291,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"個M字真係象徵乳房喎"},{"pid":"3c4dbfde010a778dc020fe3c9074387f6968df42","tid":1137291,"uid":240954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e42a7d365e5c708db4e5f84fd3d95b4fb573b4a","tid":1137291,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"個M字真係象徵乳房喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:53:28.000Z","msg":"唉我胸細=比m記歧視?"},{"pid":"5b72d03ababbf784021ee124a6ce0498466ce6b0","tid":1137291,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c4dbfde010a778dc020fe3c9074387f6968df42","tid":1137291,"uid":240954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":